OL,3,CMum 'faces losing home' from huge
OL,4,Clegal bills after law firm went bust
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FElaine Wilcox spoke to some of the
OL,8,Fresidents affected in Burnley.
OL,10,FA mother says she is at risk of losing
OL,11,Fher home after being left with
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage
OL,13,Fand rising legal fees when a law firm
OL,14,Frepresenting her went bust.
OL,16,FSharon Lord is one of more than 80
OL,17,Fhomeowners in encouraged to sue the
OL,18,Fgovernment by SSB Law, after cavity
OL,19,Fwall insulation they had purchased
OL,20,Fusing grants in 2014 began to cause
OL,21,Fdamp and mould.
