OL,3,CMum 'faces losing home' from huge
OL,4,Clegal bills after law firm went bust
OL,6,FThe law firm told her the damages
OL,7,Fcould amount to as much as #50,000,
OL,8,Fand promised to represent her on a no
OL,9,Fwin no fee basis.
OL,11,FBut when SSB Law went bust in January
OL,12,F2024, the single mother-of-two was
OL,13,Fleft to pay more than #17,000 in legal
OL,14,Ffees - alongside around 1,500 other
OL,15,Fproperty owners who had been
OL,16,Frepresented by the law firm.
OL,18,FShe is now joining calls to halt their
OL,19,Frising legal costs, left over as a
OL,20,Fresult of the company going bust.
