OL,3,CMum 'faces losing home' from huge
OL,4,Clegal bills after law firm went bust
OL,6,FShe said: "You trust the Government,
OL,7,Fthey're the people who are supposed to
OL,8,Fhelp and as far as we were aware they
OL,9,Fwere vetting these people.
OL,11,F"But they came in and did so much
OL,12,Fdamage to thousands of properties."
OL,14,FNew solicitors have taken up Sharon's
OL,15,Fcase, which have stopped her legal
OL,16,Ffees rising for now.
OL,18,FDiane Longworth, also from Burnley,
OL,19,Fwas forced to spend her life savings
OL,20,Fon a #7,000 legal bill she was told
OL,21,Fshe would never have to pay.
