OL,6,FShe said: "It was a week before
OL,7,FChristmas, and I opened it and i
OL,8,Fdidn't know what it was about. I've
OL,9,Fnever been in debt.
OL,11,F"I just had nearly had a heart attack,
OL,12,Fmy heart was beating so fast."
OL,14,FDiane was also being represented by
OL,15,FSSB Law, after they told her the wrong
OL,16,Ffoam insulation had been used on her
OL,17,Fproperty.
