OL,6,FShe said: "I'd like everybody to not
OL,7,Fhave to pay for something they thought
OL,8,Fwas right - and I'd like my money
OL,9,Fback."
OL,11,FHer calls were echoed by Solicitor
OL,12,FErich Kurtz.
OL,14,FHe said: "What has to happen is the...
OL,15,Finsurers for SSB Law or the insurers
OL,16,Fin the underlying claim - one of those
OL,17,Ftwo needs to pay."
