OL,6,FA spokesperson from the Solicitors
OL,7,FRegulation Authority said: "We are
OL,8,Faware of the concerns of many
OL,9,Fhouseholders. We are investigating
OL,10,Fwhether SSB Group acted appropriately
OL,11,Fin these cases. We will take action
OL,12,Fagainst solicitors if we find they
OL,13,Fhave fallen short of the standards we
OL,14,Fexpect.
OL,16,F"If there has been negligence, those
OL,17,Faffected may wish to consider getting
OL,18,Flegal advice as they may be able to
OL,19,Fmake a claim on the firm's insurance.
